```go
type GitIngestionPayload struct {
	RepositorySource string `json:"repository_source"`
	Actor string `json:"actor,omitempty"`
	Verbosity int `json:"verbosity"`
	NoDeps bool `json:"no_deps,omitempty"`

}
```

</td>
<td>

```typescript
export interface GitIngestionPayload {
  /**
   * RepositorySource can be a local path OR a URL (handler will clone if URL)
   */
  repository_source: string;
  actor?: string;
  verbosity: number;
  no_deps?: boolean;
  /**
   * Since filters commits to only those after this timestamp or commit hash
   */
  since?: string;
}
```

```go
type RepoSource struct {
	LocalPath string
	OriginalInput string
	IsCloned bool

}
```

</td>
<td>

```typescript
export interface RepoSource {
  /**
   * LocalPath is the path to the local repository (either original or fetched)
   */
  LocalPath: string;
  /**
   * OriginalInput is the original input (URL or path)
   */
  OriginalInput: string;
  /**
   * IsCloned indicates if the repo was fetched from a remote source
   */
  IsCloned: boolean;
  /**
   * TempDir is the temporary directory used for fetching (empty if local)
   */
  TempDir: string;
}
```

</td>
</tr>
</table>
